John,

Today is our Dad's 53rd Birthday!

Birthdays are the best days of the year in our home. Mom and Dad always go 
out of their way to make sure it's something special for each of us.

This year, we want to do something to make it special for him. We want to 
send him a card signed by all of the supporters he has across the country.

Will you sign a Birthday card for our Dad?

He has been working so hard these past months traveling all across the 
country talking about his vision for our future. We grew up seeing Dad 
work nonstop to improve the community around us, and to better the lives 
of the people of Maryland. We know he will do the same for all Americans 
as President.
